headline: Domino’s Pizza, Inc. (DPZ): A Bull Case Theory

headline: Warren Buffett's New Favorite Stock to Buy -- a 7,000%-Gainer Since Its IPO -- May Be Wall Street's Newest Stock-Split Stock in 2025
summary: The beloved consumer brand recently purchased by the Oracle of Omaha has skyrocketed by roughly 7,000% since its public debut 20 years ago.
